00:11:16.700 --> 00:11:21.700
but his blood, notice again, will I require at thine hand.

00:11:22.120 --> 00:11:25.080
Nevertheless, if thou warn the righteous man

00:11:25.080 --> 00:11:28.000
that the righteous sin not, and he doth not sin,

00:11:28.000 --> 00:11:30.520
he shall surely live because he is warned.

00:11:30.520 --> 00:11:34.640
Also thou hast delivered thy soul.

00:11:34.640 --> 00:11:36.640
And the hand of the Lord was there upon me.

00:11:36.640 --> 00:11:39.240
And he said unto me, arise, go forth into the plain,

00:11:39.240 --> 00:11:42.320
