00:11:42.320 --> 00:11:43.960
And so here in Ezekiel chapter three,

00:11:43.960 --> 00:11:45.920
in verses 16 through 22,

00:11:45.920 --> 00:11:49.200
God provides for us this responsibility

00:11:49.200 --> 00:11:52.000
given to Ezekiel as a watchman.

00:11:52.000 --> 00:11:54.640
But as we look in Acts chapter number 20,

00:11:54.640 --> 00:11:56.360
